<DOCNO> FBIS4-29119 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "dreas115__a94021" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-EAS-94-115-A </AU>
Daily Report 
<DATE1>  15 June 1994 </DATE1>

