<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["'Civilian Defense Training' in S. Korea" -- KCNA headline] </F>
  [Text] Pyongyang, June 16 (KCNA) -- The puppets staged a 
large-scale "civilian defense training" all over South Korea 
Wednesday by mobilising a great number of people, according to 
radio reports from Seoul. 
  They kicked up a dust with training of taking shelter and 
training under simulated conditions of "chemical, biological and 
radioactive attack" under an imaginary "emergency state." 
  The South Korean bellicose elements blared that it was a 
training of taking shelter in the wartime "to be prepared 
against the situation caused by the 'nuclear issue' of the 
North." 
  Earlier, the puppets announced that a massive military 
exercise will be staged involving various means of war, with 6.5 
million men of the "civilian defense" forces and even U.S. 
troops present in South Korea participating in the training in 
the future. 
  The U.S. imperialists and the South Korean puppets are 
frequently staging war drills with increasing intensity, driving 
the situation on the Korean peninsula to the extreme pitch of 
strain. This indicates that their war hysterics to stifle the 
North has reached a very reckless stage. 

</TEXT>

