<F P=102>   SK1606081594 Pyongyang Korean Central Broadcasting Network 
in Korean 2200 GMT 15 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK1606081594 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang Korean Central Broadcasting Network 
in Korean 2200 GMT 15 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=105> Korean </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Timed to coincide with its attempt to further drive 
the situation on the Korean peninsula onto the brink of war with 
the U.S. imperialists by finding faults with our fictitious 
nuclear issue, the South Korean puppets staged a game with a 
large-scale civil defense drill across South Korea on 15 June by 
dragging out thousands of residents, according to radio reports 
from Seoul. 
  The puppets made a stir by blowing warning sirens at 1405 
all 
over places in South Korea and staging an evacuation drill 
preparing for all contingencies. In addition, the puppets ran 
amok in staging a drill simulating chemical, biological, and 
nuclear attacks in every place. 
  The South Korean warmongers incited war fever by babbling 
that the drill has been restored as a war time evacuation 
exercise to prepare for contingencies in the wake of the North 
Korean nuclear issue. 
  Prior to this, the puppets announced that in future drills, 
not only some 6.5 million reserve forces but also the U.S. 
Forces in South Korea will be mobilized and that it will wage a 
large-scale war exercise using various types of war equipment. 
  The U.S. imperialists and the South Korean puppets are 
continuously staging war exercises and increasing their degree 
by extremely heightening tension on the Korean peninsula. This 
shows that the rascals' war hysteria attempting to crush us has 
reached an extremely reckless stage. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

