<H3> <TI>   Anniversary of Kim Chong-il WPK Work Marked </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Anniversary of Kim Chong-il WPK Work Marked </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Ministry of Armed Forces Seminar </H4>

<F P=102> SK1606044894 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0432 GMT 16 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1606044894 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, June 16 (KCNA) -- A seminar of the 
Ministry of People's Armed Forces was held Wednesday to 
commemorate the 30th anniversary of the start of work by Comrade 
Kim Chong-il, Supreme Commander of the Korean People's Army, at 
the Central Committee of the Workers' Party of Korea [WPK]. 
  Choe Kwang, Politburo member of the C.C. [Central 
Committee], 
the WPK and chief of the General Staff of the KPA [Korean 
People's Army], and several other generals made speeches on the 
subjects including "Holding in high esteem respected Supreme 
Commander Comrade Kim Chong-il at the head of our party is 
historical event which brought great switchover in accomplishing 
the revolutionary cause of chuche," "Great leadership of 
respected Supreme Commander Comrade Kim Chong-il in making the 
whole Army crystal of singlehearted unity." 
  The speakers said that today all the officers and men of the 
People's Army have grown up to be loyal subjects and filial 
soldiers resolutely defending the party and the leader at the 
cost of their lives and the People's Army strengthened and 
developed into the invincible revolutionary Armed Forces capable 
of defeating any formidable enemy at one stroke. This is 
entirely a noble fruition of the great leadership of Comrade Kim 
Chong-il, Supreme Commander of the Korean People's Army, they 
stressed. 
  Noting that the last 30-year course of the People's Army is 
shining as proud annals in which the singlehearted unity of the 
whole Army centering on the great brilliant commander has been 
cemented as firm as a rock and has emerged victorious with its 
might, they pointed out that the supreme commander has 
resolutely defended the traditions of the singlehearted unity 
and more firmly realized the ideological and purposeful unity of 
the whole Army centering on the leader from the first period of 
his leadership over the revolutionary Armed Forces. 
  The speakers said that Comrade Kim Chong-il has strengthened 
and developed the revolutionary Armed Forces into a true army of 
the leader and the party. 
  They stressed that the People's Army is exalting its might 
as 
a powerful a-match-for-a-hundred army thanks to the great 
brilliant commander Comrade Kim Chong-il's chuche-based idea of 
army building and his extraordinary leadership, and herein lie 
his undying feats which will shine for ages with the victorious 
advance of the revolutionary cause of chuche. 

</TEXT>

