<H3> <TI>   Defense Ministry Plans To Give Daily Briefing </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Defense Ministry Plans To Give Daily Briefing </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK1606023894 Seoul YONHAP in English 0231 GMT 16 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1606023894 </F>
<F P=104>  Seoul YONHAP </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Seoul, June 16 (YONHAP) -- The Defense Ministry said 
Thursday it will hold a daily press briefing to keep ordinary 
citizens abreast of the military situation and help dispel 
public anxiety. The daily press briefings will continue until 
the current crisis is resolved, officials said. 

</TEXT>

